A Love Song for Bobby Long;;2004;;R;;Drama;;7.1;;Shainee Gabel;;Scarlett Johansson,John Travolta,Gabriel Macht,Deborah Kara Unger,Dane Rhodes,David Jensen,Clayne Crawford,Sonny Shroyer,Carol Sutton,Walter Breaux,Warren Kole,Bernard Johnson,Gina 'Ginger' Bernal,Douglas M. Griffin,Earl Maddox,Steve Maye,Don Brady,Will Barnett;;A young woman, Pursy (played by Scarlett Johansson), learns that her estranged mother has died in New Orleans. She returns to her mother's house to discover that it is inhabited by two men, one an aging alcoholic, Bobby Long (John Travolta).;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0369672/